---
import { SITE } from '../consts';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import AdSlot from '../components/ads/AdSlot.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description={`About ${SITE.name} — free, fast and private online calculators, converters and generators that run entirely in your browser.`}
>
  <div class="container" style="max-width: 760px; padding: 2rem 1.25rem 3rem;">
    <h1>About {SITE.name}</h1>
    <section class="prose">
      <p>
        {SITE.name} is a collection of free, fast and private online tools — calculators, converters
        and generators — built to do one thing well: give you an accurate answer in seconds, on any
        device, without asking you to sign up or hand over personal data.
      </p>

      <h2>How it works</h2>
      <p>
        Almost every tool runs entirely in your browser (client-side). Your inputs are never sent to
        a server, which means calculations are instant and your data stays on your device. There are
        no accounts, no trackers, and no paywalls.
      </p>

      <h2>Why we built it</h2>
      <p>
        Most calculator sites are cluttered, slow, or buried in ads. We designed {SITE.name} to be
        clean, accessible and exceptionally fast, with a strong focus on search-engine best practices
        and Core Web Vitals so the page is ready the moment you need it.
      </p>

      <h2>Accuracy &amp; responsibility</h2>
      <p>
        Our calculators provide estimates for educational and planning purposes. They are not a
        substitute for professional financial, tax, legal or medical advice. Always verify important
        decisions with a qualified professional.
      </p>

      <h2>Get in touch</h2>
      <p>Questions, corrections or tool requests? Visit our <a href="/contact/">contact page</a>.</p>
    </section>

    <AdSlot id="inContent" label="Advertisement" />
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
